The paper discusses the design of an incentive mechanism for energy harvesting-based IoT systems, which involves wireless communication and information theory (cs.IT), networking and communication protocols for IoT (cs.NI), game theory for incentive design (cs.GT), control and optimization for system performance (cs.SY), and contract theory for efficient information exchange (cs.MA).
